## Conceptual inspiration

lecode draws architectural inspiration from several open-source agent-management projects, notably Paseo (AGPL-3.0). Per clean-room practice, no source code or prose from AGPL projects has been incorporated into this repository. Concept extraction occurs via the SPEC/ process — see SPEC/README.md.

## Code lineage

Portions of lecode's Rust code are ported from the lesearch repository (Apache-2.0, same author) with attribution retained where applicable.
